{"title":"炮弹之谜","authors":["天马"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":4,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮弹之谜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在所谓“达赖喇嘛的声明”里说，“3月17日，迫击炮朝着罗布林卡宫打了两三炮。幸而炮弹都落到附近的一个池塘里去了。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尼赫鲁说，“……据声明（按即所谓达赖喇嘛的声明）说那些炮弹或者什么东西落在他的宫殿上……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池塘和宫殿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相距不很远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有天把话拉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"互相问寒暖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宫殿先说话："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“老兄可危险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听说你的家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落下三炮弹”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池塘听此言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞪起一双眼："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“老兄开玩笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说话失检点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我家很平安，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从未落炮弹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倒是我听说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你家遭灾难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说你运不好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身上中炮弹；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或者啥东西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落在你上面。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宫殿打哈哈："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是胡扯淡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你眼又不瞎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看我可健全？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么怪东西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那样玄又玄？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看又看不到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听又听不见！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说完一席话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彼此心放宽："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮弹及其他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来是胡编！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}